            "metadata": {
                "abstract": "We present CCPlotR-an R package that generates visualizations of cell-cell interactions. CCPlotR is designed to work with the output of tools that predict cell-cell interactions from single-cell gene expression data and requires only a table of predicted interactions as input. The package can generate a comprehensive set of publication-ready figures such as heatmaps, dotplots, circos plots and network diagrams, providing a useful resource for researchers working on cell-cell interactions.",
